msgstr "Uf..."

msgctxt "1688_Noa"
msgid "Akiyama-san! How's the water over there?"
msgstr "¡Akiyama-san! ¿Cómo está el agua por allí?"

msgctxt "1700_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, hey, Noa-chan. It's pretty damn great."
msgstr "Oh, hola Noa-chan. El agua está condenadamente buena."

msgctxt "1772_amb_onsen"
msgid "Whew! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> That was a great bath..."
msgstr "¡Uf! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Ese baño estuvo genial..."

msgctxt "1784_Noa"
msgid "But I couldn't help thinking about that stalker thing, so I couldn't really relax..."
msgstr "Pero no podía dejar de pensar en ese tema del acosador, así que no podía relajarme..."

msgctxt "1796_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, I can understand. You might be worryin' about them staring at you in the bath, that kind of thing."
msgstr "Sí, lo entiendo. Debes estar preocupada de que te miren en el baño, ese tipo de cosas."

msgctxt "1808_Noa"
msgid "Yeah. I know I might be worrying about this too much, but..."
msgstr "Sí. Sé que podría estar preocupándome demasiado por esto, pero..."

msgctxt "1820_Noa"
msgid "That's why this was the first time in a long time I could have a nice, relaxing bath."
msgstr "Por eso esta fue la primera vez en mucho tiempo que pude disfrutar de un buen baño relajante."

msgctxt "1832_Akiyama"
msgid "Why don't we come here every day? It's close to the workplace. Not a bad idea, huh?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no venimos aquí todos los días? Está cerca del trabajo. No es mala idea, ¿no?"

msgctxt "1844_Noa"
msgid "If we went here every day, we'd drain our wallets pretty quickly..."
msgstr "Si viniéramos aquí todos los días, vaciaríamos nuestras billeteras bastante rápido..."

msgctxt "1856_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah, I guess you have a point."
msgstr "Sí, supongo que tienes un punto."

msgctxt "1868_Noa"
msgid "But then I'd feel like I would be letting the stalker win, and that would suck!"
msgstr "Pero entonces sentiría que estaría dejando ganar al acosador, ¡y eso apestaría!"

msgctxt "1880_Noa"
msgid "Why should I change my whole lifestyle when he's the one in the wrong!? That's just crazy!"
msgstr "¿Por qué debería cambiar todo mi estilo de vida cuando él es el que está equivocado? ¡Eso es una locura!"

msgctxt "1892_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah. Guess that means you should be more confident about going out and stuff. If worse comes to worst, I'll save you."
msgstr "Sí. Supongo que eso significa que deberías tener más confianza para salir y esas cosas. En el peor de los casos, te salvaré."

msgctxt "1904_Noa"
msgid "Haha. ♪ I feel much safer now! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Thanks, Akiyama-san. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ja, ja. ♪ ¡Ahora me siento mucho más segura! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Gracias, Akiyama-san. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "1916_Akiyama"
msgid "You never know. He could show up here, too."
msgstr "Nunca se sabe. Podría aparecer aquí también."

msgctxt "1928_Akiyama"
msgid "You've always got to be careful."
msgstr "Uno siempre tiene que tener cuidado."

msgctxt "1940_Noa"
msgid "Really...? C'mon, don't scare me..."
msgstr "¿En serio...? Vamos, no me asuste..."

msgctxt "1952_Akiyama"
msgid "Don't worry, you've got me around. right? If anything happens, I'll be there to protect you."
msgstr "No te preocupes, me tienes cerca, ¿verdad? Si pasa algo, estaré ahí para protegerte."

msgctxt "1964_Noa"
msgid "I guess, but... Ugh, I'm freaked out now..."
msgstr "Supongo, pero... Ugh, ahora estoy asustada..."

msgctxt "1976_Noa"
msgid "Akiyama-san, you're the worst..."
msgstr "Akiyama-san, eres el peor..."

msgctxt "1988_Akiyama"
msgid "Sorry..."
msgstr "Lo siento..."

msgctxt "2000_Akiyama"
msgid "I'll find him. He thinks he's in control right now, that's why he's so confident."
msgstr "Lo encontraré. Cree que está en control de la situación, por eso está tan confiado."

msgctxt "2012_Akiyama"
msgid "If you start to go on the offensive, he might turn tail and run off."
msgstr "Si comienzas a pasar a la ofensiva, es posible que se acobarde y salga corriendo."

msgctxt "2024_Noa"
msgid "There's no way I could do something like that... Akiyama-san, is that really how little you care about me?"
msgstr "De ninguna manera podría hacer algo así... Akiyama-san, ¿de verdad le importo tan poco?"

msgctxt "2036_Akiyama"
msgid "That's not true. But that could be a way to deal with those kinds of guys, right?"
msgstr "No es verdad. Pero esa podría ser una forma de lidiar con ese tipo de personas, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "2048_Noa"
msgid "No way! Geez, I should have never told you about it..."
msgstr "¡No puede ser! Cielos, nunca debí habérselo dicho..."

msgctxt "2060_Akiyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "2072_amb_onsen"
msgid "Akiyama-san! I've got a fun hot spring fact for you!"
msgstr "¡Akiyama-san! ¡Tengo un dato divertido sobre las aguas termales para usted!"

msgctxt "2084_Akiyama"
msgid "Well, that came out of nowhere. Sure, let's hear it."
msgstr "Bueno, eso surgió de la nada. Claro, escuchémoslo."

msgctxt "2096_Noa"
msgid "Did you know that there are hot springs..."
msgstr "¿¡Sabías que hay aguas termales..."

msgctxt "2108_Noa"
msgid "...on the <Italic>moon</Italic>!?"
msgstr "...en la <Italic>luna</Italic>!?"

msgctxt "2120_Noa"
msgid "Well? Isn't that crazy!?"
msgstr "¿Y bien? ¿¡No es eso muy loco!?"

msgctxt "2132_Akiyama"
msgid "That is pretty crazy. Hot springs on the moon... gives off a pretty romantic feeling, huh."
msgstr "Eso es bastante loco. Aguas termales en la luna... da una sensación bastante romántica, eh."

msgctxt "2144_Noa"
msgid "Right!? When I found out about it, I was totally moved!"
msgstr "¿Verdad? Cuando me enteré, ¡me emocioné muchisimo!"

msgctxt "2156_Akiyama"
msgid "The fact that that made you feel so much emotion just goes to show that you've got a girly side, Noa-chan."
msgstr "El hecho de que eso te haya emocionado tanto demuestra que tienes un lado femenino, Noa-chan."

msgctxt "2168_Noa"
msgid "I mean, I am a girl! I've gotta show you that girly side of me sometimes."
msgstr "Quiero decir, ¡soy una chica! A veces tengo que mostrarle mi lado femenino."

msgctxt "2180_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, so you're telling me this was all planned out? Well, that's scary."
msgstr "¿Me estás diciendo que todo esto estaba planeado? Bueno, eso da miedo."

msgctxt "2192_Akiyama"
msgid "(Huh? Was it really the moon, though? I feel like that's off... Well, whatever.)"
msgstr "(¿Eh? ¿Era realmente la luna, sin embargo? Siento que eso está mal... Bueno, lo que sea)"

msgctxt "2204_Akiyama"
msgid "It's not that crazy. It was a long time ago that they proved the possibility of water existing on the surface of the moon."
msgstr "No es tan descabellado. Hace mucho tiempo que demostraron la posibilidad de que existiera agua en la superficie de la Luna."

msgctxt "2216_Akiyama"
msgid "If that water got a little warmer, you could call it a hot spring, I guess."
msgstr "Si esa agua se calentara un poco, se podría decir que es una fuente termal, supongo."

msgctxt "2228_Noa"
msgid "I wasn't trying to start a confusing conversation with you... I shouldn't have said anything in the first place."
msgstr "No era mi intención iniciar una conversación confusa con usted... No debería haber dicho nada en primer lugar."

msgctxt "2240_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, sorry. I just like talking about stuff like this. I can't stop running my mouth."
msgstr "Oh, lo siento. Es que me gusta hablar de estas cosas. No puedo evitar hablar sin parar."

msgctxt "2252_Akiyama"
msgid "Huh? Wait, are you sure it was the moon? I think I heard it was actually Mars..."
msgstr "¿Eh? Espera, ¿estás segura de que era la luna? Creo haber oído que en realidad era Marte..."

msgctxt "2264_Noa"
msgid "Geez, Akiyama-san!"
msgstr "¡Cielos, Akiyama-san!"

msgctxt "2276_Akiyama"
msgid "Sorry, sorry, hahaha."
msgstr "Lo siento, lo siento, ja, ja, ja."

msgctxt "2288_Akiyama"
msgid "I think you are getting it wrong, though. I saw something on the news about Mars and hot springs."
msgstr "Sin embargo, creo que te estás equivocando. Vi algo en las noticias sobre Marte y las aguas termales."

msgctxt "2300_Noa"
msgid "Huh? Really?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿En serio?"

msgctxt "2312_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah. What was it... something about magma warming up underground water deposits and creating big clouds of silicon dioxide that they discovered."
msgstr "Sí. Qué era... algo sobre magma calentando depósitos de agua subterráneos y creando grandes nubes de dióxido de silicio que descubrieron."

msgctxt "2324_Noa"
msgid "...I don't understand a word you're saying. Silicon... what? What is that?"
msgstr "... No entiendo ni una palabra de lo que dices. Silicio... ¿Qué? ¿Qué es eso?"

msgctxt "2336_Noa"
msgid "*sigh* I can't believe I'm mixing up the moon and Mars. I'm really dumb..."
msgstr "*suspiro* No puedo creer que esté confundiendo la Luna con Marte. Soy tan tonta..."

msgctxt "2348_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh. It is a pretty big mistake to make, mixing up the moon and Mars."
msgstr "Je. Es un error bastante grande, mezclar a la Luna y a Marte."

msgctxt "2360_Noa"
msgid "Ugh..."
msgstr "Ugh..."

msgctxt "2372_Akiyama"
msgid "But it's a good thing you're interested in that stuff, don't you think? If you like something, you'll end up remembering it eventually."
msgstr "Pero es algo bueno que te interesen ese tipo de cosas, ¿no crees? Si algo te gusta, al final acabarás recordándolo."

msgctxt "2384_Noa"
msgid "...You're right! Yes! Hehe, you sure know how to make things right with a follow-up comment."
msgstr "...You're right! Yes! Hehe, you sure know how to make things right with a follow-up comment."

msgctxt "2456_Akiyama"
msgid "Man, going to the hot springs is just the best. My whole body feels great."
msgstr "Ir a las aguas termales es lo mejor. Todo mi cuerpo se siente genial."

msgctxt "2468_Noa"
msgid "Geez, Akiyama-san, you sound like an old man! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Cielos, Akiyama-san, suena como un anciano! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2480_amb_onsen"
msgid "Speak for yourself. You're not going to be young forever."
msgstr "Habla por ti. No vas a ser joven para siempre."

msgctxt "2492_Noa"
msgid "Too bad! I'm still growing, you know!"
msgstr "¡Qué pena! Todavía estoy creciendo, ¡sabe!"

msgctxt "2504_Noa"
msgid "Even my chest has gotten a little bigger lately. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Incluso mis pechos han crecido un poco últimamente. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2516_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr "Oh..."

msgctxt "2528_Akiyama"
msgid "(...Noa-chan's chest is still growing, huh...)"
msgstr "(...Los pechos de Noa-chan siguen creciendo, ¿eh...)"

msgctxt "2540_amb_onsen"
msgid "Really? You think so? Well, I guess I am getting to that age where you wouldn't be surprised if I had kids."
msgstr "¿De verdad? ¿Eso crees? Bueno, supongo que estoy llegando a esa edad en la que no te sorprendería si tuviera hijos."

msgctxt "2552_Noa"
msgid "Ahaha! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I've got this weird image of you taking a bath with your kids... It's so weird. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ja, ja, ja <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Tengo una imagen rara de usted bañándose con sus hijos... Es tan raro. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "2564_Noa"
msgid "Come to think of it, when I was a little kid, I used to take baths with my dad..."
msgstr "Ahora que lo pienso, cuando era pequeña, solía bañarme con mi papá..."

msgctxt "2576_Akiyama"
msgid "That so?"
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "2588_Akiyama"
msgid "(...Taking a bath with Noa-chan...)"
msgstr "(...Tomar un baño con Noa-chan...)"

msgctxt "2636_Akiyama"
msgid "(No, no, what am I thinking about!?)"
msgstr "(No, no, ¿en qué estoy pensando?)"

msgctxt "2648_Noa"
msgid "Okay, Akiyama-san, I'm gonna get out."
msgstr "Bueno, Akiyama-san, ya voy a salir."

msgctxt "2696_Noa"
msgid "Akiyama-san! Are you even listening to me?"
msgstr "¡Akiyama-san! ¿Me está escuchando?"

msgctxt "2708_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, yeah, I am."
msgstr "Oh, sí, lo estoy."

msgctxt "2720_Noa"
msgid "Okay, I'm gonna get out now."
msgstr "Bueno, voy a salir ahora."

msgctxt "2732_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay. I guess I'll get out, too."
msgstr "Bueno, entonces yo también saldré."

msgctxt "2780_Player"
msgid "Whew..."
msgstr "Uf..."

msgctxt "2816_Erena"
msgid "Akiyama-san! How's the water over there?"
msgstr "¡Akiyama-san! ¿Cómo está el agua por allí?"

msgctxt "2828_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, hey, Erena-chan. It's pretty damn great."
msgstr "Oh, hey, Erena-chan. It's pretty damn great."

msgctxt "2888_amb_onsen"
msgid "I'm kinda impatient, huh? I'm super impatient with baths."
msgstr "I'm kinda impatient, huh? I'm super impatient with baths."

msgctxt "2900_Akiyama"
msgid "Can't lounge around and relax?"
msgstr "Can't lounge around and relax?"

msgctxt "2912_Erena"
msgid "Yeah. Somehow when I'm just lying still in the bathtub, I start getting really antsy."
msgstr "Yeah. Somehow when I'm just lying still in the bathtub, I start getting really antsy."

msgctxt "2924_Akiyama"
msgid "That's awful... You made the effort to come out to this nice hot springs, you should at least be able to relax and enjoy it a little."
msgstr "That's awful... You made the effort to come out to this nice hot springs, you should at least be able to relax and enjoy it a little."

msgctxt "2936_Erena"
msgid "Yeah, I get that, but... to tell the truth, I'm already itchin' to get out."
msgstr "Yeah, I get that, but... to tell the truth, I'm already itchin' to get out."

msgctxt "2948_Akiyama"
msgid "Man, seriously? We haven't even been in here for 5 minutes."
msgstr "Man, seriously? We haven't even been in here for 5 minutes."

msgctxt "2960_Erena"
msgid "I like taking baths and stuff, but... What should I do?"
msgstr "I like taking baths and stuff, but... What should I do?"

msgctxt "2972_Akiyama"
msgid "Guess you'll just have to deal with that part of your personality forever..."
msgstr "Guess you'll just have to deal with that part of your personality forever..."

msgctxt "2984_Akiyama"
msgid "I guess I'll get out quick, then. I wouldn't want to force you to stay in longer than you want."
msgstr "I guess I'll get out quick, then. I wouldn't want to force you to stay in longer than you want."

msgctxt "2996_Erena"
msgid "Aww, you'd do that for me? <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> You're such a gentleman, Akiyama-san. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Aww, you'd do that for me? <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> You're such a gentleman, Akiyama-san. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "3008_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh, plus, I want to see what you look like when you've just gotten out of the bath."
msgstr "Heh, plus, I want to see what you look like when you've just gotten out of the bath."

msgctxt "3020_Erena"
msgid "Ahaha! Sure. I'll let you get your fill of my pearly white just-out-of-the-bath skin. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ahaha! Sure. I'll let you get your fill of my pearly white just-out-of-the-bath skin. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "3032_Akiyama"
msgid "Looking forward to it."
msgstr "Te estaremos esperando."

msgctxt "3044_Akiyama"
msgid "You don't feel that way with me, right?"
msgstr "You don't feel that way with me, right?"

msgctxt "3056_Erena"
msgid "Yeah, about that, sorry, but I've been itching to get out of the bath this whole time."
msgstr "Yeah, about that, sorry, but I've been itching to get out of the bath this whole time."

msgctxt "3068_Erena"
msgid "I can't change this part of my personality that easily..."
msgstr "I can't change this part of my personality that easily..."

msgctxt "3080_Akiyama"
msgid "Maybe you shouldn't have come here to the hot springs..."
msgstr "Maybe you shouldn't have come here to the hot springs..."

msgctxt "3092_amb_onsen"
msgid "I heard that the water here is really good for your skin. That's why I'm glad I came today."
msgstr "I heard that the water here is really good for your skin. That's why I'm glad I came today."

msgctxt "3104_Akiyama"
msgid "Guess it makes it worth it, then."
msgstr "Guess it makes it worth it, then."

msgctxt "3116_Erena"
msgid "Oh hey, do you know about the Three Big Beauty Hot Springs?"
msgstr "Oh hey, do you know about the Three Big Beauty Hot Springs?"

msgctxt "3128_Akiyama"
msgid "Everyone loves those \"Whatever Number Big Whatever\" stuff. Guess it's no different for hot springs."
msgstr "Everyone loves those \"Whatever Number Big Whatever\" stuff. Guess it's no different for hot springs."

msgctxt "3140_Erena"
msgid "Yeah! Umm, I think the first one's Yunokawa Springs in Shimane. Then there's Kawanaka Springs in Gunma..."
msgstr "Yeah! Umm, I think the first one's Yunokawa Springs in Shimane. Then there's Kawanaka Springs in Gunma..."

msgctxt "3152_Erena"
msgid "Huh? What was the last one..."
msgstr "Huh? What was the last one..."

msgctxt "3164_Akiyama"
msgid "It's Ryujin Springs in Wakayama, right? The one that the old lords liked to go to way back in the day."
msgstr "It's Ryujin Springs in Wakayama, right? The one that the old lords liked to go to way back in the day."

msgctxt "3176_Erena"
msgid "Yes! That's the one! I thought you were just pretending to be interested, but you actually do know!"
msgstr "Yes! That's the one! I thought you were just pretending to be interested, but you actually do know!"

msgctxt "3188_Akiyama"
msgid "Eh, it's just something I know, not really too common knowledge."
msgstr "Eh, it's just something I know, not really too common knowledge."

msgctxt "3200_Erena"
msgid "C'mon, don't try to be humble. I bet you know a bunch of good hot springs! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> You better tell me about them sometime. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "C'mon, don't try to be humble. I bet you know a bunch of good hot springs! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> You better tell me about them sometime. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "3212_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh, all right."
msgstr "Ah, está bien."

msgctxt "3224_Akiyama"
msgid "Isn't it Kusatsu Springs in Gunma? That one's pretty famous."
msgstr "Isn't it Kusatsu Springs in Gunma? That one's pretty famous."

msgctxt "3236_Erena"
msgid "Oh, no, that's not it. It's one of the Three Famous Japanese Springs, though."
msgstr "Oh, no, that's not it. It's one of the Three Famous Japanese Springs, though."

msgctxt "3248_Akiyama"
msgid "See, what'd I tell you? There's another Big Three whatever."
msgstr "See, what'd I tell you? There's another Big Three whatever."

msgctxt "3260_Erena"
msgid "Ugh, I had it right on the tip of my tongue, but now I can't move past Kusatsu!"
msgstr "Ugh, I had it right on the tip of my tongue, but now I can't move past Kusatsu!"

msgctxt "3272_Erena"
msgid "This is all your fault, Akiyama-san!"
msgstr "This is all your fault, Akiyama-san!"

msgctxt "3284_Akiyama"
msgid "She got mad at me..."
msgstr "She got mad at me..."

msgctxt "3296_Erena"
msgid "Oh, that's it! I got it! It's Ryujin Springs in Wakayama! Geez, you were so off, Akiyama-san."
msgstr "Oh, that's it! I got it! It's Ryujin Springs in Wakayama! Geez, you were so off, Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "3308_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, was that it? I mean, I knew what it was. I was going between that one and Kusatsu."
msgstr "Oh, was that it? I mean, I knew what it was. I was going between that one and Kusatsu."

msgctxt "3320_Erena"
msgid "Uh-huh. We'll just leave it at that."
msgstr "Uh-huh. We'll just leave it at that."

msgctxt "3332_Akiyama"
msgid "It's Hakone Springs in Kanagawa, right? It's pretty close by, but it's famous."
msgstr "It's Hakone Springs in Kanagawa, right? It's pretty close by, but it's famous."

msgctxt "3344_Erena"
msgid "No, that's not it. That's in the Three Big Spring Towns, though."
msgstr "No, that's not it. That's in the Three Big Spring Towns, though."

msgctxt "3356_Akiyama"
msgid "How many Big Threes are there...?"
msgstr "How many Big Threes are there...?"

msgctxt "3368_Erena"
msgid "Ugh, what was it? I need to know!"
msgstr "Ugh, what was it? I need to know!"

msgctxt "3380_Akiyama"
msgid "Can it wait? You can just look it up on your phone."
msgstr "Can it wait? You can just look it up on your phone."

msgctxt "3392_Erena"
msgid "Ugh, I gotta know, though..."
msgstr "Ugh, I gotta know, though..."

msgctxt "3404_Erena"
msgid "Oh, that's it! I got it! It's Ryujin Springs in Wakayama! Geez, you were so off, Akiyama-san."
msgstr "Oh, that's it! I got it! It's Ryujin Springs in Wakayama! Geez, you were so off, Akiyama-san."

msgctxt "3416_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, was that it? I mean, I knew what it was. I was going between that one and Hakone."
msgstr "Oh, was that it? I mean, I knew what it was. I was going between that one and Hakone."

msgctxt "3428_Erena"
msgid "Uh-huh. We'll just leave it at that."
msgstr "Uh-huh. We'll just leave it at that."

msgctxt "3500_Akiyama"
msgid "Man, going to the hot springs is just the best. My whole body feels great."
msgstr "Ir a las aguas termales es lo mejor. Todo mi cuerpo se siente genial."

msgctxt "3512_Erena"
msgid "Geez, Akiyama-san, you sound like an old man! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Cielos, Akiyama-san, suena como un anciano! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "3524_amb_onsen"
msgid "I mean, I am getting old. My shoulders get pretty stiff sometimes. Erena, why don't you come over here and wash this old man's back?"
msgstr "I mean, I am getting old. My shoulders get pretty stiff sometimes. Erena, why don't you come over here and wash this old man's back?"

msgctxt "3536_Erena"
msgid "Ahaha! You seriously are old!"
msgstr "Ahaha! You seriously are old!"

msgctxt "3548_Erena"
msgid "Sure! Once you get a little older and are really an old man, I'll wash your back every day."
msgstr "Sure! Once you get a little older and are really an old man, I'll wash your back every day."

msgctxt "3560_Akiyama"
msgid "Aww, what, you can't do that for me now?"
msgstr "Aww, what, you can't do that for me now?"

msgctxt "3572_Akiyama"
msgid "(...Erena-chan washing my back...)"
msgstr "(...Erena-chan washing my back...)"

msgctxt "3584_amb_onsen"
msgid "Really? You think so? Well, I guess I am getting to that age where you wouldn't be surprised if I had kids."
msgstr "¿De verdad? ¿Eso crees? Bueno, supongo que estoy llegando a esa edad en la que no te sorprendería si tuviera hijos."

msgctxt "3596_Erena"
msgid "Ahaha! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I've got this weird image of you taking a bath with your kids... It's so weird. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ja, ja, ja <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Tengo una imagen rara de usted bañándose con sus hijos... Es tan raro. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "3608_Erena"
msgid "Come to think of it, when I was a little kid, I used to take baths with my dad..."
msgstr "Ahora que lo pienso, cuando era pequeña, solía bañarme con mi papá..."

msgctxt "3620_Akiyama"
msgid "That so?"
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "3632_Akiyama"
msgid "(...Taking a bath with Erena-chan...)"
msgstr "(...Taking a bath with Erena-chan...)"

msgctxt "3680_Akiyama"
msgid "(No, no, what am I thinking about!?)"
msgstr "(No, no, ¿en qué estoy pensando?)"

msgctxt "3692_Erena"
msgid "Akiyama-san, I'm gonna get out."
msgstr "Akiyama-san, voy a salir."

msgctxt "3740_Erena"
msgid "Geez, Akiyama-san! Are you even listening?"
msgstr "¡Cielos, Akiyama-san! ¿Acaso está escuchándome?"

msgctxt "3752_Akiyama"
msgid "O-oh, yeah, I am."
msgstr "Oh, sí, lo estoy."

msgctxt "3764_Erena"
msgid "Okay, I'm gonna get out."
msgstr "Bien, voy a salir."

msgctxt "3776_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay. I guess I'll get out, too."
msgstr "Bueno, entonces yo también saldré."

msgctxt "3824_Player"
msgid "Whew..."
msgstr "Uf..."

msgctxt "3860_Chihiro"
msgid "Tanimura-san! How's the water over there?"
msgstr "¡Tanimura-san! ¿Cómo está el agua por ahí?"

msgctxt "3872_Tanimura"
msgid "Hey, Chihiro-chan. Feels great."
msgstr "Oh, hola Chihiro-chan. El agua está genial."

msgctxt "3932_amb_onsen"
msgid "Ahh. ♪ Ahh... ♪"
msgstr "Ahh. ♪ Ahh... ♪"

msgctxt "3944_Tanimura"
msgid "...What are you doing?"
msgstr "... ¿Qué estás haciendo?"

msgctxt "3956_Chihiro"
msgid "Vocal exercises! ♪ My voice always sounds so nice in the bath with the echo, so I like to have a little fun with it."
msgstr "¡Ejercicios vocales! ♪ Mi voz suena muy agradable con el eco del baño, así que me gusta divertirme con eso."

msgctxt "3968_Chihiro"
msgid "Hey, you should do them with me, Tanimura-san!"
msgstr "Oiga, ¡debería hacerlo conmigo, Tanimura-san!"

msgctxt "3980_Tanimura"
msgid "Hey now, why are you roping me into this?"
msgstr "Oye, ¿por qué me estás metiendo en eso?"

msgctxt "3992_Chihiro"
msgid "Aw, come on! I can't see your face, so it's not like it's gonna be embarrassing or anything. C'mon! One, two, three, go!"
msgstr "¡Oh, vamos! No puedo verle el rostro, así que no es como si fuese a ser vergonzoso o algo así. ¡Vamos! ¡Un, dos, tres, va!"

msgctxt "4004_Tanimura"
msgid "Ahh. ♪ Ahh... ♪"
msgstr "Ahh. ♪ Ahh... ♪"

msgctxt "4016_Chihiro"
msgid "Oooh! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> You've got a pretty nice voice, Tanimura-san! I'm kind of surprised. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Aaah! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> ¡Qué gran voz tiene, Tanimura-san! Estoy sorprendida. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "4028_Tanimura"
msgid "Really? I never noticed it before."
msgstr "¿De verdad? Nunca me había dado cuenta."

msgctxt "4040_Chihiro"
msgid "Really? You've got such a nice voice! I'm surprised you don't practice! I'm so jealous."
msgstr "¿Ah, sí? ¡Estoy sorprendida de que no practiques! ¡Tienes una voz muy bonita! Ay, que envidia le tengo."

msgctxt "4052_Chihiro"
msgid "Okay! I'm gonna practice hard and make my voice sound even better!"
msgstr "¡Bien! ¡Voy a practicar mucho y haré que mi voz suene aún mejor!"

msgctxt "4064_Tanimura"
msgid "Heh, good luck."
msgstr "Je, buena suerte."

msgctxt "4076_Tanimura"
msgid "You're so cute. I'd be too embarrassed to practice singing in the bath."
msgstr "Eres muy adorable. Yo tendría mucha vergüenza de cantar en el baño."

msgctxt "4088_Chihiro"
msgid "It's not embarrassing at all! Even my grandpa likes to hum a little song in the bath!"
msgstr "¡No hay nada de que avergonzarse! ¡Incluso a mi abuelo le gusta tararear alguna cancioncita en el baño!"

msgctxt "4100_Chihiro"
msgid "Wait, Tanimura-san, are you just a terrible singer?"
msgstr "Un segundo, eso quiere decir... Tanimura-san, ¿acaso es usted un cantante terrible?"

msgctxt "4112_Tanimura"
msgid "No, it's not that..."
msgstr "No, no es eso..."

msgctxt "4124_Chihiro"
msgid "Oh, I think I just hit the bull's-eye!"
msgstr "Ah, ¡parece que le di justo en el clavo, eh!"

msgctxt "4136_Tanimura"
msgid "I said it's not that..."
msgstr "Ya te dije que no es eso..."

msgctxt "4148_Tanimura"
msgid "I'd rather you do something else for me."
msgstr "Preferiría que hicieras otra cosa por mí."

msgctxt "4160_Chihiro"
msgid "Huh? What is it?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Qué cosa?"

msgctxt "4172_Tanimura"
msgid "You said before that you do kabuki, right? Wouldn't it be so powerful in here, with all the echoing?"
msgstr "Habías dicho que hacías kabuki, ¿verdad? ¿No sonaría poderoso hacerlo aquí con todo el eco que hay?"

msgctxt "4184_Chihiro"
msgid "Oh, is that it? Sure! Ahem!"
msgstr "Ah, ¿solo eso? ¡Seguro! ¡Ajam!"

msgctxt "4196_Chihiro"
msgid "Hear me, traveler! You who stand before the gate!"
msgstr "¡Escuchadme, viajero! ¡Vos que os plantáis ante la gran puerta!"

msgctxt "4208_Chihiro"
msgid "How was that?"
msgstr "¿Qué le pareció?"

msgctxt "4220_Tanimura"
msgid "Man, that sounded so different. Thanks for that performance."
msgstr "Vaya, eso sonó muy diferente. Gracias por la actuación."

msgctxt "4232_Chihiro"
msgid "Hehe! Thank you!"
msgstr "¡Je, je! ¡Gracias!"

msgctxt "4244_Chihiro"
msgid "Huh? Wait, I told you to do vocal exercises, but somehow it's become all about me... No fair!"
msgstr "¿Eh? Espera, le dije que hiciera ejercicios vocales, pero de alguna manera termino tratándose todo sobre mí... ¡No es justo!"

msgctxt "4256_Tanimura"
msgid "Hehehe."
msgstr "Je, je, je."

msgctxt "4268_amb_onsen"
msgid "There are a lot of great writers who love hot springs."
msgstr "Hay muchos buenos escritores a los que les encantan las aguas termales."

msgctxt "4280_Tanimura"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr "¿De verdad?"

msgctxt "4292_Chihiro"
msgid "Yeah, like Dazai Osamu, and Naoya Shiga... Oh, and I heard Natsume Soseki liked hot springs, too!"
msgstr "Sí, como Dazai Osamu y Naoya Shinga... ¡Ah, y también escuché que a Natsume Soseki también le gustaban las aguas termales!"

msgctxt "4304_Chihiro"
msgid "I love reading, so whenever I think of hot springs, I can't help but think of those great authors."
msgstr "Me encanta leer, así que siempre que pienso en las aguas termales no puedo evitar pensar en aquellos grandes autores."

msgctxt "4316_Tanimura"
msgid "Don't hot springs attract crime? They're practically magnets for illegal activity."
msgstr "¿Las aguas termales no atraen al crimen? Son básicamente un imán para las actividades ilegales."

msgctxt "4328_Chihiro"
msgid "Oh yeah, those Steam Room Something-Something Murder Incidents! That's a staple for any detective TV show."
msgstr "¡Ah, sí, los asesinatos en las salas de vapor! Son todo un clásico en las series de detectives."

msgctxt "4340_Tanimura"
msgid "Then at the very end, the detective corners the suspect on a cliff and reveals the truth... No detective wouldn't be entranced by a scene like that."
msgstr "Y al final de la historia el detective arrincona al sospechoso en un acantilado y revela toda la verdad... No existe ni un detective que no quede fascinado por una escena así."

msgctxt "4352_Chihiro"
msgid "Yeah. I wanna put on a performance that makes someone feel inspired!"
msgstr "Sí. ¡Me gustaría hacer una escena en la que alguien se sienta inspirado!"

msgctxt "4364_Tanimura"
msgid "Well then, you've got to practice a lot and get a lot of good experience under your belt."
msgstr "Bueno, entonces debes practicar mucho y obtener mucha experiencia en tu camino."

msgctxt "4376_Chihiro"
msgid "Right! I'll give it my all!"
msgstr "¡Cierto! ¡Daré lo mejor de mí!"

msgctxt "4388_Tanimura"
msgid "All I think of is those sexy bath scenes in TV shows. I mean, I'm a guy, so..."
msgstr "En lo único que pienso es en las series donde hay escenas sexis en los baños. Soy un hombre, así que..."

msgctxt "4400_Chihiro"
msgid "Bath scenes... Couldn't you have a more romantic image in mind when you think of hot springs?"
msgstr "Escenas de baño... ¿No podría tener alguna imagen más romántica cuando piensa en las aguas termales?"

msgctxt "4412_Tanimura"
msgid "What're you talking about? If you become an actress, you'll have to do those kinds of scenes, won't you?"
msgstr "¿De qué hablas? Si te haces actriz, tendrás que hacer esa clase de escenas, ¿no?"

msgctxt "4424_Chihiro"
msgid "Well yeah, but... I still don't like it!"
msgstr "Bueno, sí, pero... ¡Aun así no me gusta!"

msgctxt "4436_Chihiro"
msgid "Here I thought you were a lot more serious than that, Tanimura-san..."
msgstr "Y yo que pensaba que usted era mucho más serio, Tanimura-san..."

msgctxt "4448_Tanimura"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "4460_Tanimura"
msgid "I think of great myths and legends."
msgstr "Pienso en grandes mitos y leyendas."

msgctxt "4472_Chihiro"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr "¿De verdad?"

msgctxt "4484_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, like Tamatsukuri Springs in Shimane, which is said to have been discovered by the god Sukunahikona-no-Mikoto."
msgstr "Sí, como las aguas termales de Tamatsukuri en Shimane, se dice que fue descubierto por el mismísimo dios Sakunahikona-no-Mikoto."

msgctxt "4496_Tanimura"
msgid "It's pretty interesting how hot springs were around back in the time of gods. It makes hot springs feel really special."
msgstr "Es muy interesante saber como eran las aguas termales en la época de los dioses, hacen que se sientan muy especiales."

msgctxt "4508_Chihiro"
msgid "That's kinda cool! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Don't tell me you're a big reader too, Tanimura-san."
msgstr "Sí, ¡es tan genial! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> No me diga que usted también es un lector, Tanimura-san."

msgctxt "4520_Tanimura"
msgid "Not at all! I just happened to read it in a book, that's all."
msgstr "¡Para nada! Lo leí en un libro, nada más."

msgctxt "4532_Chihiro"
msgid "Haha. ♪ You should give me some recommendations sometime!"
msgstr "Ja, ja. ♪ ¡Debería recomendarme alguno para leer de vez en cuando!"

msgctxt "4544_Tanimura"
msgid "Sure, sounds great."
msgstr "Claro, porque no."

msgctxt "4616_Tanimura"
msgid "Man, going to hot springs is just the best. My whole body feels great."
msgstr "Uf. Ir a las aguas termales es de lo mejor. Todo mi cuerpo se siente increíble."

msgctxt "4628_Chihiro"
msgid "Geez, Tanimura-san, you sound like an old man! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ay, Tanimura-san. ¡Habla como un anciano! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "4640_amb_onsen"
msgid "I mean, I'm not that young anymore. Chihiro, come wash this old man's back for him, will you?"
msgstr "Bueno, ya no soy tan joven. Chihiro, ¿por qué no le lavas la espalda a este ancianito? ¿Podrías?"

msgctxt "4652_Chihiro"
msgid "Ahaha! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> You don't have to act all old all of a sudden!"
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> ¡No tiene que fingir ser un anciano tan repentinamente!"

msgctxt "4664_Chihiro"
msgid "But okay! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Once you get old and gray, I'll wash your back every day, Tanimura-san."
msgstr "¡Pero acepto! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Cuando sea un viejito y tenga todo el pelo gris, le lavaré la espalda todos los días, Tanimura-san."

msgctxt "4676_Tanimura"
msgid "Aww, what, you can't do that for me now?"
msgstr "Uhm, pero, ¿no podrías hacer eso hacerlo ahora?"

msgctxt "4688_Tanimura"
msgid "(...Chihiro-chan washing my back...)"
msgstr "(...Chihiro-chan está lavando mi espalda...)"

msgctxt "4700_amb_onsen"
msgid "That's not true. I'm still a hot-blooded young man."
msgstr "Eso no es cierto. Todavía soy un joven de sangre caliente."

msgctxt "4712_Chihiro"
msgid "Ahaha! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> No matter how young you might be, though, don't go doing something immature like trying to peek on me."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> No importa lo joven que sea, ni se le ocurra hacer algo tan inmaduro como intentar espiarme."

msgctxt "4724_Tanimura"
msgid "I wouldn't do anything like that. I'm not a dumb kid."
msgstr "Nunca haría algo como eso. No soy un estúpido niño."

msgctxt "4736_Chihiro"
msgid "I'm just kidding! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Hehehe. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Solo bromeo! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Je, je, je. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "4748_Tanimura"
msgid "(...Should I peek on Chihiro-chan in the bath...?)"
msgstr "(...Mmm, ¿debería espiar a Chihiro-chan en el baño?...)"

msgctxt "4796_Tanimura"
msgid "(No, no, what am I thinking about!?)"
msgstr "(No, no, ¿en qué estoy pensando?)"

msgctxt "4808_Chihiro"
msgid "Okay, Tanimura-san, I'm gonna get out."
msgstr "Bueno, Tanimura-san, ya voy a salir."

msgctxt "4856_Chihiro"
msgid "Geez, Tanimura-san! Are you even listening?"
msgstr "Dios, ¡Tanimura-san! ¿Me está escuchando?"

msgctxt "4868_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, I'm listening."
msgstr "Sí, sí. Te escuchó."

msgctxt "4880_Chihiro"
msgid "Okay, I'm gonna get out now."
msgstr "Bueno, voy a salir ahora."

msgctxt "4892_Tanimura"
msgid "Okay. I guess I'll get out, too."
msgstr "Está bien, entonces yo también saldré."

msgctxt "4940_Player"
msgid "Whew..."
msgstr "Uf..."

msgctxt "4976_Maya"
msgid "Kiryu-san! How's the water over there?"
msgstr "Kiryu-san! How's the water over there?"

msgctxt "4988_Kiryu"
msgid "Hey, Maya. Feeling pretty good over here."
msgstr "Hey, Maya. Feeling pretty good over here."

msgctxt "5048_amb_onsen"
msgid "I love baths! I never knew this little hole-in-the-wall\\r\n"\n"was here! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I love baths! I never knew this little hole-in-the-wall\\r\n"\n"was here! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5060_Kiryu"
msgid "Guess inviting you here was a good idea."
msgstr "Guess inviting you here was a good idea."

msgctxt "5072_Maya"
msgid "Yup! Thanks, Kiryu-san."
msgstr "Yup! Thanks, Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "5084_Maya"
msgid "Oh, but you've gotta be careful in the bath."
msgstr "Oh, but you've gotta be careful in the bath."

msgctxt "5096_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh? Careful about what?"
msgstr "Huh? Careful about what?"

msgctxt "5108_Maya"
msgid "The longer you're in the bath, the more you sweat, right?"
msgstr "The longer you're in the bath, the more you sweat, right?"

msgctxt "5120_Maya"
msgid "And when you sweat, you get dehydrated, and that can be bad for your skin."
msgstr "And when you sweat, you get dehydrated, and that can be bad for your skin."

msgctxt "5132_Maya"
msgid "So no matter how long I want to stay in the bath, I've gotta keep it to twenty minutes! That's what I've decided."
msgstr "So no matter how long I want to stay in the bath, I've gotta keep it to twenty minutes! That's what I've decided."

msgctxt "5144_Kiryu"
msgid "You're pretty careful about a lot of things. Whoever said a model's work is easy?"
msgstr "You're pretty careful about a lot of things. Whoever said a model's work is easy?"

msgctxt "5156_Maya"
msgid "I know, right? The cameras at work are super high def, so if my skin is even a little off, it'll totally pick up on it!"
msgstr "I know, right? The cameras at work are super high def, so if my skin is even a little off, it'll totally pick up on it!"

msgctxt "5168_Kiryu"
msgid "Still, the fact that you're always aware of that and doing what you can to control it just goes to show you how much of a professional you are. That's a rare quality."
msgstr "Still, the fact that you're always aware of that and doing what you can to control it just goes to show you how much of a professional you are. That's a rare quality."

msgctxt "5180_Maya"
msgid "Hehe. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> It's nice of you to say that."
msgstr "Hehe. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> It's nice of you to say that."

msgctxt "5192_Maya"
msgid "Okay, I'm going to give it my all, so I can spend some fun time with you as a hostess, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr "Okay, I'm going to give it my all, so I can spend some fun time with you as a hostess, Kiryu-san!"

msgctxt "5204_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, thanks for that."
msgstr "Heh, thanks for that."

msgctxt "5216_Kiryu"
msgid "Spend a little longer in the bath, just for today."
msgstr "Spend a little longer in the bath, just for today."

msgctxt "5228_Maya"
msgid "I wish I could, but... I'm a model. If my skin gets a little out of whack, it'll show up in all the pictures."
msgstr "I wish I could, but... I'm a model. If my skin gets a little out of whack, it'll show up in all the pictures."

msgctxt "5240_Maya"
msgid "Then my stylist will get mad at me... *sigh* I wish I could just soak in the bath without having to worry about all that stuff..."
msgstr "Then my stylist will get mad at me... *sigh* I wish I could just soak in the bath without having to worry about all that stuff..."

msgctxt "5252_Kiryu"
msgid "You sure go through a lot..."
msgstr "You sure go through a lot..."

msgctxt "5264_Kiryu"
msgid "You can get in the cold water bath, you know. Then you won't get sweaty. There's nothing bad about it."
msgstr "You can get in the cold water bath, you know. Then you won't get sweaty. There's nothing bad about it."

msgctxt "5276_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, but I want to get in a normal warm bath..."
msgstr "Yeah, but I want to get in a normal warm bath..."

msgctxt "5288_Maya"
msgid "Plus, spending a long time in a cold bath is just as bad for your skin, you know?"
msgstr "Plus, spending a long time in a cold bath is just as bad for your skin, you know?"

msgctxt "5300_Kiryu"
msgid "Really? I'd be totally fine in cold water. Could even do a cold waterfall."
msgstr "Really? I'd be totally fine in cold water. Could even do a cold waterfall."

msgctxt "5312_Maya"
msgid "Geez! Women aren't built that tough, you know! Are you making fun of me, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr "Geez! Women aren't built that tough, you know! Are you making fun of me, Kiryu-san?"

msgctxt "5324_amb_onsen"
msgid "Did you know that the water here is really good for your skin?"
msgstr "Did you know that the water here is really good for your skin?"

msgctxt "5336_Kiryu"
msgid "Really? It felt kind of slimy. Is that what makes it good for your skin?"
msgstr "Really? It felt kind of slimy. Is that what makes it good for your skin?"

msgctxt "5348_Maya"
msgid "Yes! It's a sodium bicarbonate hot spring. These kinds of hot springs have been called \"The Waters of Beauty\" for hundreds of years."
msgstr "Yes! It's a sodium bicarbonate hot spring. These kinds of hot springs have been called \"The Waters of Beauty\" for hundreds of years."

msgctxt "5360_Kiryu"
msgid "It'll help you be beautiful."
msgstr "It'll help you be beautiful."

msgctxt "5372_Maya"
msgid "What do you mean by that?"
msgstr "¿Qué quieres decir?"

msgctxt "5384_Kiryu"
msgid "I mean, you said it was the Waters of Beauty, so they'd make you beautiful..."
msgstr "I mean, you said it was the Waters of Beauty, so they'd make you beautiful..."

msgctxt "5396_Maya"
msgid "Kiryu-san, you have no tact at all, do you!?"
msgstr "Kiryu-san, you have no tact at all, do you!?"

msgctxt "5408_Maya"
msgid "You should've said something like, \"You're already beautiful!\" You realize what you just implied, right!? That I'm not beautiful!?"
msgstr "You should've said something like, \"You're already beautiful!\" You realize what you just implied, right!? That I'm not beautiful!?"

msgctxt "5420_Kiryu"
msgid "...Oh."
msgstr "...Oh."

msgctxt "5432_Maya"
msgid "You need to learn how to speak to women, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr "You need to learn how to speak to women, Kiryu-san!"

msgctxt "5444_Kiryu"
msgid "Well then, maybe you can teach me a few things."
msgstr "Well then, maybe you can teach me a few things."

msgctxt "5456_Maya"
msgid "Hehe! Sure. I'm going to give you a thorough education, okay? <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Hehe! Sure. I'm going to give you a thorough education, okay? <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5468_Kiryu"
msgid "You'll really stand out then. If you get any more beautiful, the police will start stopping you."
msgstr "You'll really stand out then. If you get any more beautiful, the police will start stopping you."

msgctxt "5480_Maya"
msgid "Ahaha! I wouldn't want that! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ahaha! I wouldn't want that! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5492_Maya"
msgid "It's your fault for bringing me here, so you'd better take responsibility and keep me safe!"
msgstr "It's your fault for bringing me here, so you'd better take responsibility and keep me safe!"

msgctxt "5504_Kiryu"
msgid "Is that how it works?"
msgstr "Is that how it works?"

msgctxt "5516_Maya"
msgid "Yup, that's how it works!"
msgstr "Yup, that's how it works!"

msgctxt "5528_Kiryu"
msgid "Wonder if it'll have any effect on me."
msgstr "Wonder if it'll have any effect on me."

msgctxt "5540_Maya"
msgid "I bet it will! Nowadays, there are lots of guys who are looking after their appearance."
msgstr "I bet it will! Nowadays, there are lots of guys who are looking after their appearance."

msgctxt "5552_Kiryu"
msgid "That right?"
msgstr "Con que así fue."

msgctxt "5564_Maya"
msgid "Yeah, my male model friends all take care of their appearance for work."
msgstr "Yeah, my male model friends all take care of their appearance for work."

msgctxt "5576_Maya"
msgid "Ahaha! Though it might be kind of weird to see your skin looking all silky smooth."
msgstr "Ahaha! Though it might be kind of weird to see your skin looking all silky smooth."

msgctxt "5588_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, I guess."
msgstr "Heh, I guess."

msgctxt "5660_Kiryu"
msgid "Hot springs are great. It feels like all the exhaustion is melting off my body."
msgstr "Hot springs are great. It feels like all the exhaustion is melting off my body."

msgctxt "5672_Maya"
msgid "Geez, Kiryu-san, you sound like an old man! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Geez, Kiryu-san, you sound like an old man! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5684_amb_onsen"
msgid "I suppose I'm getting to that age where it wouldn't be weird for me to have a kid."
msgstr "I suppose I'm getting to that age where it wouldn't be weird for me to have a kid."

msgctxt "5696_Maya"
msgid "Ahaha! It might be a bit weird to see you taking a bath with a little kid."
msgstr "Ahaha! It might be a bit weird to see you taking a bath with a little kid."

msgctxt "5708_Maya"
msgid "Come to think of it, when I was a little kid, I used to take baths with my dad..."
msgstr "Ahora que lo pienso, cuando era pequeña, solía bañarme con mi papá..."

msgctxt "5720_Maya"
msgid "And I get dizzy super fast when I get in the bath, so I can't stay in the bath long. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "And I get dizzy super fast when I get in the bath, so I can't stay in the bath long. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "5732_Kiryu"
msgid "That right?"
msgstr "Con que así fue."

msgctxt "5744_Kiryu"
msgid "(Maya gets dizzy really easily, huh...)"
msgstr "(Maya gets dizzy really easily, huh...)"

msgctxt "5756_amb_onsen"
msgid "That's not true at all. I'm still in my prime."
msgstr "That's not true at all. I'm still in my prime."

msgctxt "5768_Maya"
msgid "Ahaha! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> No matter how young you might be, though, don't go doing something immature like trying to peek on me."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> No importa lo joven que sea, ni se le ocurra hacer algo tan inmaduro como intentar espiarme."

msgctxt "5780_Kiryu"
msgid "Hold on, you really think I'd do something like that?"
msgstr "Hold on, you really think I'd do something like that?"

msgctxt "5792_Maya"
msgid "I'm just kidding! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I bet you were really chill when you were younger, Kiryu-san."
msgstr "I'm just kidding! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I bet you were really chill when you were younger, Kiryu-san."

msgctxt "5804_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh..."
msgstr "Je..."

msgctxt "5816_Kiryu"
msgid "(...Should I peek on Maya in the bath...)"
msgstr "(...Should I peek on Maya in the bath...)"

msgctxt "5864_Kiryu"
msgid "(No, no, what am I thinking about!?)"
msgstr "(No, no, ¿en qué estoy pensando?)"

msgctxt "5876_Maya"
msgid "Kiryu-san, I'm gonna get out."
msgstr "Kiryu-san, I'm gonna get out."

msgctxt "5924_Maya"
msgid "Geez, Kiryu-san! Are you even listening?"
msgstr "Geez, Kiryu-san! Are you even listening?"

msgctxt "5936_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah, I'm listening."
msgstr "Sí, sí. Te escuchó."

msgctxt "5948_Maya"
msgid "Okay, I'm gonna get out now."
msgstr "Bueno, voy a salir ahora."

msgctxt "5960_Kiryu"
msgid "Okay. I guess I'll get out, too."
msgstr "Bueno, entonces yo también saldré."

msgctxt "6008_Player"
msgid "Whew..."
msgstr "Uf..."

msgctxt "6044_Rio"
msgid "Akiyama-san! How's the water over there?"
msgstr "¡Akiyama-san! ¿Cómo está el agua por allí?"

msgctxt "6056_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, hey, Rio-chan. It's pretty damn great."
msgstr "Oh, hola Rio-chan. El agua está condenadamente buena."

msgctxt "6092_amb_onsen"
msgid "Hehehe..."
msgstr "Je, je, je..."

msgctxt "6104_Akiyama"
msgid "Huh? What? What's up?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Qué? ¿Qué sucede?"

msgctxt "6116_Rio"
msgid "Akiyama-san, are you mentally prepared?"
msgstr "Akiyama-san, ¿esta mentalmente preparado?"

msgctxt "6128_Akiyama"
msgid "Huh? Prepared for what?"
msgstr "¿Eh? ¿Preparado para qué?"

msgctxt "6140_Rio"
msgid "Oh, come on. Prepared for our table tennis match after we get out!"
msgstr "¡Vamos! ¡Preparado para nuestro partido de ping-pong después de salir de aquí!"

msgctxt "6152_Rio"
msgid "I'm already getting into the right mood! Gotta focus if I'm gonna beat you!"
msgstr "¡Ya estoy entrando en el estado de ánimo adecuado! ¡Tengo que concentrarme si quiero ganarle!"

msgctxt "6164_Akiyama"
msgid "I'm ready to take you on."
msgstr "Estoy listo para enfrentarte."

msgctxt "6176_Rio"
msgid "You sure? You just asked me what I was talking about, though!"
msgstr "¿Seguro? ¡Pero si hace un momento me pregunto de qué estaba hablando!"

msgctxt "6188_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh... Right."
msgstr "Oh... Cierto."

msgctxt "6200_Rio"
msgid "Don't tell me I'm the only one getting excited about this..."
msgstr "No me diga que soy la única que se esta emocionando con esto..."

msgctxt "6212_Akiyama"
msgid "That's not true! I'll have you know, I've been practicing quite a lot! I'm sorry, but I won't be holding back when I play you!"
msgstr "¡No es verdad! Que sepas que he estado practicando bastante. Y lo siento, ¡pero no me voy a contener cuando juegue contra ti!"

msgctxt "6224_Rio"
msgid "Oh! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Is that so? Well, right back at you, then!"
msgstr "¡Oh! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> ¿De verdad? ¡Pues lo mismo digo!"

msgctxt "6236_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh, looking forward to it."
msgstr "Heh, looking forward to it."

msgctxt "6248_Akiyama"
msgid "It's just a game. Let's take it easy and have fun."
msgstr "Es solo un juego. Tomémoslo con calma y divirtámonos."

msgctxt "6260_Rio"
msgid "Oh, please! You're so naive, Akiyama-san! You've always got to give it 100 percent, whether at work or at play! That's what makes it fun!"
msgstr "¡Por favor! ¡Usted es muy inocente, Akiyama-san! Siempre hay que dar el 100%, tanto en el trabajo como en el juego. ¡Eso es lo que lo hace divertido!"

msgctxt "6272_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, huh. I guess you could say that, yeah."
msgstr "Oh, eh. Supongo que se podría decir eso, sí."

msgctxt "6284_Rio"
msgid "Right? So take back what you just said and come at me with everything you've got!"
msgstr "¿Verdad? ¡Pues retire lo que acaba de decir y venga a mí con todo lo que tenga!"

msgctxt "6296_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh, all right."
msgstr "Ah, está bien."

msgctxt "6308_Akiyama"
msgid "What'll you do for me if I win?"
msgstr "¿Qué harás por mí si gano?"

msgctxt "6320_Rio"
msgid "Oh? Think you've already won, huh? I see you've already underestimated me."
msgstr "¿Oh? ¿Ya da por hecho que ha ganado, eh? Veo que ya me ha subestimado."

msgctxt "6332_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh, just so you know, I'm not gonna let you beat me."
msgstr "Je, solo para que lo sepas, no voy a dejar que me venzas."

msgctxt "6344_Rio"
msgid "Oooh, is that so? I'm gettin' all fired up now!"
msgstr "Oooh, ¿ah, sí? ¡Ahora sí que me estoy motivando!"

msgctxt "6356_Akiyama"
msgid "So, what'll you do for me if I win?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿qué harás por mí si gano?"

msgctxt "6368_Rio"
msgid "Geez, Akiyama-san, is that all you think about!?"
msgstr "Cielos, Akiyama-san, ¿¡es que eso es lo único en lo que piensa!?"

msgctxt "6380_Rio"
msgid "Hehehe, fine! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> If you win, I'll think about it."
msgstr "Je, je, je, ¡está bien! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Si me gana… lo pensaré."

msgctxt "6392_amb_onsen"
msgid "Mmm, this feels so good! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I wish I could bring my dog in with me."
msgstr "Mmm, ¡esto se siente tan bien! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Ojalá pudiera traer a mi perro conmigo."

msgctxt "6404_Akiyama"
msgid "What? You'd bring your pet into a hot spring?"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿Llevarías a tu mascota a las aguas termales?"

msgctxt "6416_Rio"
msgid "There are ryokan－you know, those traditional inns－with hot springs that will let you take your pet in with you. I've been seeing them more and more nowadays."
msgstr "Hay ryokan —sabe, esas posadas tradicionales— con aguas termales que te permiten entrar con tu mascota. Últimamente, las veo cada vez más."

msgctxt "6428_Rio"
msgid "When I went to a hot spring in Izu, I got to go in with my dog! He was so happy..."
msgstr "Cuando fui a unas aguas termales en Izu, ¡pude entrar con mi perro! Estaba tan feliz..."

msgctxt "6440_Akiyama"
msgid "Huh..."
msgstr "Huh..."

msgctxt "6452_Akiyama"
msgid "What a spoiled dog."
msgstr "Qué perro más mimado."

msgctxt "6464_Rio"
msgid "He sure is! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I spoil my little sweetie rotten."
msgstr "He sure is! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I spoil my little sweetie rotten."

msgctxt "6476_Akiyama"
msgid "He's got himself a good owner. I'm jealous."
msgstr "Tiene una dueña que lo cuida muy bien. Me da un poco de envidia."

msgctxt "6488_Rio"
msgid "You're jealous of my dog? Hehehe. Akiyama-san, you're kind of immature, huh?"
msgstr "¿Está celoso de mi perro? Je, je, je. Akiyama-san, usted es un poco inmaduro, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "6500_Akiyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "6512_Akiyama"
msgid "Going on a hot spring trip with Rio-chan... Sounds really nice. I wish I were that dog."
msgstr "Un viaje a las aguas termales con Rio-chan… suena muy bien. Desearía ser ese perro."

msgctxt "6524_Rio"
msgid "Oh! Geez, Akiyama-san, you're thinking of something dirty again, aren't you!?"
msgstr "¡Oh! Cielos, Akiyama-san, ¿¡está pensando en cosas sucias otra vez, no es así!?"

msgctxt "6536_Akiyama"
msgid "Come on, you said you go into the bath with your dog. Any man would want to join you for a dip in the hot spring."
msgstr "Vamos, dijiste que entras al baño con tu perro. Cualquier hombre querría bañarse contigo en las aguas termales."

msgctxt "6548_Rio"
msgid "Too bad! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> That bath was a special one for dogs, so you couldn't have joined me!"
msgstr "¡Qué lástima! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> ¡Ese baño era especial para perros, así que no habría podido acompañarme!"

msgctxt "6560_Akiyama"
msgid "Aww, darn."
msgstr "Aww, maldicion."

msgctxt "6572_Rio"
msgid "Don't be so down about it! We're at a hot spring together right now, right?"
msgstr "¡No se ponga así! Ahora mismo estamos juntos en las aguas termales, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "6584_Akiyama"
msgid "You must really love that dog of yours."
msgstr "Debes querer mucho a ese perro tuyo."

msgctxt "6596_Rio"
msgid "I do! I just can't stop doting on him! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> He looks like an angel when he falls asleep!"
msgstr "¡Sí! ¡Simplemente no puedo dejar de adorarlo! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> ¡Parece un ángel cuando se duerme!"

msgctxt "6608_Akiyama"
msgid "Heh, he's pretty lucky to have an owner like you."
msgstr "Je, es muy afortunado de tener una dueña como tú."

msgctxt "6620_Rio"
msgid "Hehehe. I hope you find a cutie of your own someday, Akiyama-san! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> You'll fall in love at first sight."
msgstr "Hehehe. I hope you find a cutie of your own someday, Akiyama-san! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> You'll fall in love at first sight."

msgctxt "6632_Akiyama"
msgid "I'm looking forward to that day."
msgstr "Estoy deseando que llegue ese día."

msgctxt "6704_Akiyama"
msgid "Man, going to the hot springs is just the best. My whole body feels great."
msgstr "Ir a las aguas termales es lo mejor. Todo mi cuerpo se siente genial."

msgctxt "6716_Rio"
msgid "Geez, Akiyama-san, you sound like an old man! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Cielos, Akiyama-san, suena como un anciano! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "6728_amb_onsen"
msgid "Speak for yourself. You're not going to be young forever."
msgstr "Habla por ti. No vas a ser joven para siempre."

msgctxt "6740_Rio"
msgid "Too bad! I'm still growing, you know! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Qué pena! Todavía estoy creciendo, ¡sabe! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "6752_Rio"
msgid "Even my chest has gotten a little bigger lately. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Incluso mis pechos han crecido un poco últimamente. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "6764_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr "Oh..."

msgctxt "6776_Akiyama"
msgid "(...Wow. Rio-chan's chest is still growing, huh...)"
msgstr "(...Wow Los pechos de Rio-chan siguen creciendo, eh...)"

msgctxt "6788_amb_onsen"
msgid "Really? You think so? Well, I guess I am getting to that age where you wouldn't be surprised if I had kids."
msgstr "¿De verdad? ¿Eso crees? Bueno, supongo que estoy llegando a esa edad en la que no te sorprendería si tuviera hijos."

msgctxt "6800_Rio"
msgid "Ahaha! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>  Come to think of it, when I was a little kid, I used to take baths with my dad..."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>  Ahora que lo pienso, cuando era pequeña, solía bañarme con mi papá..."

msgctxt "6812_Rio"
msgid "I get dizzy super fast when I get in the bath, so my dad was always worried about me..."
msgstr "Me mareo muy rápido cuando me meto en el baño, así que mi papá siempre estaba preocupado por mí..."

msgctxt "6824_Akiyama"
msgid "That so?"
msgstr "Ya veo."

msgctxt "6836_Akiyama"
msgid "(Rio-chan gets dizzy really easily, huh...)"
msgstr "(Shizuka se marea fácilmente, eh...)"

msgctxt "6884_Akiyama"
msgid "(No, no, what am I thinking about!?)"
msgstr "(No, no, ¿en qué estoy pensando?)"

msgctxt "6896_Rio"
msgid "Okay, Akiyama-san, I'm gonna get out."
msgstr "Bueno, Akiyama-san, ya voy a salir."

msgctxt "6944_Rio"
msgid "Akiyama-san! Are you even listening to me?"
msgstr "¡Akiyama-san! ¿Me está escuchando?"

msgctxt "6956_Akiyama"
msgid "Oh, yeah, I am."
msgstr "Oh, sí, lo estoy."

msgctxt "6968_Rio"
msgid "Okay, I'm gonna get out now."
msgstr "Bueno, voy a salir ahora."

msgctxt "6980_Akiyama"
msgid "Okay. I guess I'll get out, too."
msgstr "Bueno, entonces yo también saldré."

msgctxt "7028_Player"
msgid "Whew..."
msgstr "Uf..."

msgctxt "7064_Himeka"
msgid "Tanimura-san! How's the water over there?"
msgstr "¡Tanimura-san! ¿Cómo está el agua por ahí?"

msgctxt "7076_Tanimura"
msgid "Hey, Himeka-chan. Feels great."
msgstr "Hey, Himeka-chan. Feels great."

msgctxt "7136_amb_onsen"
msgid "Mmm, this feels so good! The bath is so big, but I have it all to myself! This is the best! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Mmm, this feels so good! The bath is so big, but I have it all to myself! This is the best! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "7148_Himeka"
msgid "Whenever I go to famous hot springs, there are always people with horrible manners. I get so mad at them!"
msgstr "Whenever I go to famous hot springs, there are always people with horrible manners. I get so mad at them!"

msgctxt "7160_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, you see those sometimes. Like people who jump in the bath without washing off first..."
msgstr "Yeah, you see those sometimes. Like people who jump in the bath without washing off first..."

msgctxt "7172_Himeka"
msgid "Yeah! And people who put their towels in the bath with them, or people who talk super loud..."
msgstr "Yeah! And people who put their towels in the bath with them, or people who talk super loud..."

msgctxt "7184_Himeka"
msgid "It's like, I'm here at a hot spring, I shouldn't be this irritated! I get so much more stressed out!"
msgstr "It's like, I'm here at a hot spring, I shouldn't be this irritated! I get so much more stressed out!"

msgctxt "7196_Tanimura"
msgid "Don't you think you're letting it bother you a little too much?"
msgstr "Don't you think you're letting it bother you a little too much?"

msgctxt "7208_Tanimura"
msgid "Tourist hotspots attract all kinds of people. It's no surprise that you get a few bad eggs among them."
msgstr "Tourist hotspots attract all kinds of people. It's no surprise that you get a few bad eggs among them."

msgctxt "7220_Tanimura"
msgid "If you're going to be that bothered by them, you're going to ruin your time at the hot spring."
msgstr "If you're going to be that bothered by them, you're going to ruin your time at the hot spring."

msgctxt "7232_Himeka"
msgid "What!? Are you just blaming it on me being high strung!?"
msgstr "What!? Are you just blaming it on me being high strung!?"

msgctxt "7244_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah. It's important to be able to get over that kind of stuff, don't you think?"
msgstr "Sí. Es importante ser capaz de superar ese tipo de cosas, ¿no crees?"

msgctxt "7256_Himeka"
msgid "I know, but... No, this definitely isn't my fault! Why don't you get it, Tanimura-san?"
msgstr "Lo sé, pero... ¡No, definitivamente no es culpa mía! ¿Por qué no lo entiende, Tanimura-san?"

msgctxt "7268_Tanimura"
msgid "She sure is stubborn..."
msgstr "She sure is stubborn..."

msgctxt "7280_Tanimura"
msgid "I do some of those things sometimes..."
msgstr "I do some of those things sometimes..."

msgctxt "7292_Himeka"
msgid "Oh my gosh, really? You're awful, Tanimura-san!"
msgstr "Oh my gosh, really? You're awful, Tanimura-san!"

msgctxt "7304_Tanimura"
msgid "But I have to use the men's baths, so my doing those things wouldn't bother you at all, right?"
msgstr "But I have to use the men's baths, so my doing those things wouldn't bother you at all, right?"

msgctxt "7316_Himeka"
msgid "I don't know... If you're not considerate of others in the bath, then I doubt you'd be considerate of others outside of the bath!"
msgstr "I don't know... If you're not considerate of others in the bath, then I doubt you'd be considerate of others outside of the bath!"

msgctxt "7328_Tanimura"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr "Oh..."

msgctxt "7340_Himeka"
msgid "You better be careful from here on out, okay?"
msgstr "You better be careful from here on out, okay?"

msgctxt "7352_Tanimura"
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr "Bueno..."

msgctxt "7364_Tanimura"
msgid "That kind of behavior is unforgivable. Anyone behaves like that around me, they're getting arrested."
msgstr "That kind of behavior is unforgivable. Anyone behaves like that around me, they're getting arrested."

msgctxt "7376_Himeka"
msgid "Ahaha! You'd arrest them?"
msgstr "Ahaha! You'd arrest them?"

msgctxt "7388_Tanimura"
msgid "Himeka, if you see anyone like that, tell me right away. I'll arrest them for crimes against humanity."
msgstr "Himeka, if you see anyone like that, tell me right away. I'll arrest them for crimes against humanity."

msgctxt "7400_Himeka"
msgid "Ahaha! If you came into the girl's bath, you'd be the one getting arrested! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ahaha! If you came into the girl's bath, you'd be the one getting arrested! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "7412_amb_onsen"
msgid "...I just realized something incredible."
msgstr "...I just realized something incredible."

msgctxt "7424_Tanimura"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr "¿Qué cosa?"

msgctxt "7436_Himeka"
msgid "We're at a hot spring... A detective is here on a trip... And he's just met a mysterious woman..."
msgstr "We're at a hot spring... A detective is here on a trip... And he's just met a mysterious woman..."

msgctxt "7448_Tanimura"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "7460_Himeka"
msgid "We're about to stumble upon a grisly murder!"
msgstr "We're about to stumble upon a grisly murder!"

msgctxt "7472_Tanimura"
msgid "Tomorrow morning, they'll discover the corpse of a beautiful woman..."
msgstr "Tomorrow morning, they'll discover the corpse of a beautiful woman..."

msgctxt "7484_Himeka"
msgid "Eek! Who's the beautiful woman?"
msgstr "Eek! Who's the beautiful woman?"

msgctxt "7496_Tanimura"
msgid "Who would do such a thing... Himeka, I swear to you, I will avenge you and catch the person who did this to you!"
msgstr "Who would do such a thing... Himeka, I swear to you, I will avenge you and catch the person who did this to you!"

msgctxt "7508_Himeka"
msgid "Ahahaha! What's up with you, Tanimura-san? You're really getting into this! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ahahaha! What's up with you, Tanimura-san? You're really getting into this! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "7520_Tanimura"
msgid "Whodunit? You... done it!"
msgstr "Whodunit? You... done it!"

msgctxt "7532_Himeka"
msgid "...Hmm, see, you've got to play around with the setting a little bit more than that."
msgstr "...Hmm, see, you've got to play around with the setting a little bit more than that."

msgctxt "7544_Tanimura"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "7556_Himeka"
msgid "You jumped the gun a little bit there, Tanimura-san. But the fact that you blindly charged in to go along with my silly joke has really left a good impression on me. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "You jumped the gun a little bit there, Tanimura-san. But the fact that you blindly charged in to go along with my silly joke has really left a good impression on me. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "7568_Tanimura"
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr "Bueno..."

msgctxt "7580_Tanimura"
msgid "I met you long before today, Himeka."
msgstr "I met you long before today, Himeka."

msgctxt "7592_Himeka"
msgid "Whoa, you didn't even bite, you just shut it down!"
msgstr "Whoa, you didn't even bite, you just shut it down!"

msgctxt "7604_Himeka"
msgid "Ahaha! Man, I never thought you'd fire back with that!"
msgstr "Ahaha! Man, I never thought you'd fire back with that!"

msgctxt "7616_Himeka"
msgid "That was pretty funny, though! You've got a pretty good sense of humor, huh, Tanimura-san? I wasn't expecting that."
msgstr "That was pretty funny, though! You've got a pretty good sense of humor, huh, Tanimura-san? I wasn't expecting that."

msgctxt "7628_Tanimura"
msgid "You think so?"
msgstr "¿De verdad lo cree?"

msgctxt "7700_Tanimura"
msgid "Man, going to hot springs is just the best. My whole body feels great."
msgstr "Uf. Ir a las aguas termales es de lo mejor. Todo mi cuerpo se siente increíble."

msgctxt "7712_Himeka"
msgid "Geez, Tanimura-san, you sound like an old man! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Ay, Tanimura-san. ¡Habla como un anciano! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "7724_amb_onsen"
msgid "Well, isn't the pot calling the kettle black? You're not going to be young forever, you know."
msgstr "Well, isn't the pot calling the kettle black? You're not going to be young forever, you know."

msgctxt "7736_Himeka"
msgid "Too bad, but you're wrong! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> My body is still growing! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Too bad, but you're wrong! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> My body is still growing! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "7748_Himeka"
msgid "Even my chest has gotten a little bigger lately. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I don't need to worry about getting old anytime soon!"
msgstr "Even my chest has gotten a little bigger lately. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> I don't need to worry about getting old anytime soon!"

msgctxt "7760_Tanimura"
msgid "Oh, is that so?"
msgstr "Oh, is that so?"

msgctxt "7772_Tanimura"
msgid "(...Himeka-chan's chest is still growing, huh...)"
msgstr "(...Himeka-chan's chest is still growing, huh...)"

msgctxt "7784_amb_onsen"
msgid "That's not true. I'm still a hot-blooded young man."
msgstr "Eso no es cierto. Todavía soy un joven de sangre caliente."

msgctxt "7796_Himeka"
msgid "Ahaha! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> No matter how young you might be, though, don't go doing something immature like trying to peek on me."
msgstr "¡Ja, ja, ja! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> No importa lo joven que sea, ni se le ocurra hacer algo tan inmaduro como intentar espiarme."

msgctxt "7808_Tanimura"
msgid "I wouldn't do anything like that. I'm not a dumb kid."
msgstr "Nunca haría algo como eso. No soy un estúpido niño."

msgctxt "7820_Himeka"
msgid "I'm just kiddin'! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Hehehe. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I'm just kiddin'! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Hehehe. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "7832_Tanimura"
msgid "(...Peeking on Himeka-chan in the bath...)"
msgstr "(...Peeking on Himeka-chan in the bath...)"

msgctxt "7880_Tanimura"
msgid "(No, no, what am I thinking about!?)"
msgstr "(No, no, ¿en qué estoy pensando?)"

msgctxt "7892_Himeka"
msgid "Okay, Tanimura-san, I'm gonna get out."
msgstr "Bueno, Tanimura-san, ya voy a salir."

msgctxt "7940_Himeka"
msgid "Geez, Tanimura-san! Are you even listening?"
msgstr "Dios, ¡Tanimura-san! ¿Me está escuchando?"

msgctxt "7952_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah, I'm listening."
msgstr "Sí, sí. Te escuchó."

msgctxt "7964_Himeka"
msgid "Okay, I'm gonna get out now."
msgstr "Bueno, voy a salir ahora."

msgctxt "7976_Tanimura"
msgid "Okay. I guess I'll get out, too."
msgstr "Bueno, entonces yo también saldré."

msgctxt "8024_Player"
msgid "Whew..."
msgstr "Uf..."

msgctxt "8060_Shizuka"
msgid "Hey! How's the water over there?"
msgstr "¡Ey! ¿Cómo está el agua por allí?"

msgctxt "8072_Kiryu"
msgid "Hey, Shizuka. Feeling pretty good over here."
msgstr "Hola, Shizuka. Se siente bastante bien por aquí."

msgctxt "8132_amb_onsen"
msgid "Whew! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> That was a great bath..."
msgstr "¡Uf! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Ese baño estuvo genial..."

msgctxt "8144_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah... It's so strange that there's a hot spring bubbling up under this big entertainment district."
msgstr "Sí... Es tan extraño que haya aguas termales burbujeando bajo este gran distrito de entretenimiento."

msgctxt "8156_Shizuka"
msgid "Don't you think so, too? When I started thinking about it, I got real interested in learning about hot springs."
msgstr "¿No lo cree usted también? Cuando empecé a pensar sobre eso, me interesé mucho en aprender acerca de las aguas termales."

msgctxt "8168_Shizuka"
msgid "I went to the library to do some research, and I just couldn't stop! It was so fascinating!"
msgstr "Fui a la biblioteca a investigar y no pude parar. ¡Fue tan fascinante!"

msgctxt "8180_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, you're pretty enthusiastic about things, huh, Shizuka."
msgstr "Je, eres bastante entusiasta con las cosas, ¿eh, Shizuka?"

msgctxt "8192_Shizuka"
msgid "Hehe, perhaps."
msgstr "Jeje, tal vez."

msgctxt "8204_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh yeah, so when I was doing research, I found out about a law called the Hot Spring Law. Ever heard of it?"
msgstr "Ah, sí, mientras investigaba, encontré una ley llamada “Ley de Aguas Termales”. ¿Alguna vez ha oído hablar de eso?"

msgctxt "8216_Kiryu"
msgid "Nope, can't say I have."
msgstr "No, no puedo decir que lo haya hecho."

msgctxt "8228_Shizuka"
msgid "I don't think many people are familiar with it, but it had such a cool ring to it, I couldn't help but feel intrigued! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "No creo que muchas personas la conozcan, ¡pero tiene un nombre tan genial que no pude evitar sentirme intrigada! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8240_Shizuka"
msgid "According to the Hot Spring Law, there are a number of requirements that must be met for a spring to be called a hot spring."
msgstr "De acuerdo con la Ley de Aguas Termales, hay una serie de requisitos que deben cumplirse para que a un manantial se le considere aguas termales."

msgctxt "8252_Kiryu"
msgid "They've had a lot of places making false claims lately, huh. They need these regulations to protect the legitimate places."
msgstr "Han tenido un montón de lugares haciendo declaraciones falsas últimamente, eh. Necesitan estas regulaciones para proteger a los lugares legítimos."

msgctxt "8264_Shizuka"
msgid "Right. Here's a question for you about one of those requirements! For something to be called a hot spring, the water has to be above what temperature?"
msgstr "Exacto. ¡Le tengo una pregunta sobre uno de esos requisitos! Para que algo se considere una fuente termal, ¿a qué temperatura debe estar el agua?"

msgctxt "8276_Kiryu"
msgid "It's pretty low, right? It's 25 degrees Celsius or higher."
msgstr "Es bastante baja, ¿no? Debe ser de 25 grados Centigrados o más."

msgctxt "8288_Shizuka"
msgid "I knew you'd know it! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Even water that's not all that warm can still be considered water from a \"hot\" spring."
msgstr "¡Sabía que usted lo sabría! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Incluso el agua que no está tan caliente puede considerarse proveniente de una fuente \"termal\"."

msgctxt "8300_Shizuka"
msgid "The hot spring under this particular bathhouse is extremely hot, so they extract the water and cool it for the baths."
msgstr "La fuente termal bajo esta casa de baños en particular es extremadamente caliente, por lo que extraen el agua y la enfrían para los baños."

msgctxt "8312_Kiryu"
msgid "Wow... You really have done your research, huh."
msgstr "Vaya... Realmente investigaste bastante, ¿eh?"

msgctxt "8324_Shizuka"
msgid "Thank you! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> If I learn something new, I'll be sure to share it with you. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Gracias! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Si aprendo algo nuevo, me aseguraré de compartirlo con usted. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8336_Kiryu"
msgid "Well, it's a \"hot\" spring, so it's got to be at least 40 degrees or hotter at the source, right?"
msgstr "Bueno, es una fuente \"termal\", así que tiene que estar al menos a 40 grados o más en la fuente, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "8348_Shizuka"
msgid "I thought so too, but it's actually 25 degrees Celsius! That's all it needs to be called a hot spring."
msgstr "Yo también lo creía, pero en realidad son 25 grados Centígrados. Eso es todo lo que se necesita para que puedan llamarse aguas termales."

msgctxt "8360_Kiryu"
msgid "Really? 25 degrees isn't that much hotter than plain tap water."
msgstr "¿En serio? 25 grados, no es eso más caliente que el agua del grifo."

msgctxt "8372_Shizuka"
msgid "True. That's why springs with a colder source have to heat up the water for their customers."
msgstr "Es verdad. Por eso las fuentes con agua más fría tienen que calentarla para sus clientes."

msgctxt "8384_Kiryu"
msgid "And they still call those hot springs? That's pretty interesting."
msgstr "¿Y aun así las llaman aguas termales? Eso es bastante interesante."

msgctxt "8396_Shizuka"
msgid "Hehe, I'm glad you're so into this! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> If I learn anything new, I'll be sure to tell you."
msgstr "Je, je, ¡me alegro de que esté tan interesado en esto! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Si aprendo algo nuevo, me aseguraré de contárselo."

msgctxt "8408_Kiryu"
msgid "Spring water has to be pretty hot to be considered a hot spring. I'd guess 55 degrees or hotter?"
msgstr "El agua debe estar suficientemente caliente para ser considerada agua termal. ¿Yo diría que unos 55 grados o más?"

msgctxt "8420_Shizuka"
msgid "I thought so too, but it's actually 25 degrees Celsius! That's all it needs to be called a hot spring."
msgstr "Yo también lo creía, pero en realidad son 25 grados Centígrados. Eso es todo lo que se necesita para que puedan llamarse aguas termales."

msgctxt "8432_Kiryu"
msgid "25 degrees? How hot is that? It's hard to imagine..."
msgstr "¿25 grados? ¿Qué tan caliente es eso? Es difícil de imaginar..."

msgctxt "8444_Shizuka"
msgid "It's about as warm as a pool."
msgstr "Es igual de caliente que una piscina."

msgctxt "8456_Shizuka"
msgid "Oh, that reminds me of something from back in school! We couldn't have a pool day in P.E. if the outside and water temperature added together was greater than 50 degrees Celsius."
msgstr "Oh, ¡eso me recuerda algo de cuando iba al colegio! No podíamos tener un día de piscina en Educación Física si la temperatura exterior y la del agua sumadas superaban los 50 grados Celsius."

msgctxt "8468_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh. You sure know a lot of things, Shizuka. It's pretty impressive."
msgstr "Vaya. Sabes muchas cosas, Shizuka. Es bastante impresionante."

msgctxt "8480_Shizuka"
msgid "Thank you! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> If I learn something new, I'll be sure to share it with you. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Gracias! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Si aprendo algo nuevo, me aseguraré de compartirlo con usted. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8492_amb_onsen"
msgid "Oh, right! This hot spring is 100 percent from the source!"
msgstr "¡Oh, sí! ¡Estas aguas termales son 100% de la fuente!"

msgctxt "8504_Shizuka"
msgid "I'm really glad I get to enjoy a real hot spring in the city!"
msgstr "¡Me alegro mucho de poder disfrutar de unas auténticas aguas termales en la ciudad!"

msgctxt "8516_Kiryu"
msgid "Wow... 100 percent from the source, huh..."
msgstr "Vaya... 100% de la fuente, eh..."

msgctxt "8528_Shizuka"
msgid "Do you know what that means?"
msgstr "¿Sabe lo que eso significa?"

msgctxt "8540_Kiryu"
msgid "Huh? Oh, yeah..."
msgstr "¿Eh? Oh, sí..."

msgctxt "8552_Kiryu"
msgid "They don't dilute the source water with regular water. You can tell that the minerals must be really concentrated. Feels great."
msgstr "No diluyen el agua de la fuente con agua normal. Se nota que los minerales deben estar muy concentrados. Se siente muy bien."

msgctxt "8564_Shizuka"
msgid "...Sorry, Kiryu-san, but that's not what it means."
msgstr "... Lo siento, Kiryu-san, pero eso no es lo que significa."

msgctxt "8576_Kiryu"
msgid "Really? ...Well, then, what does it mean?"
msgstr "¿De verdad? ... Bueno, entonces, ¿qué significa?"

msgctxt "8588_Shizuka"
msgid "It means that they use the water straight from the source, and don't recycle it. They use it, then pour it down the drain. That's why it's a very luxurious experience."
msgstr "Significa que utilizan el agua directamente de la fuente y no la reciclan. La utilizan y luego la vierten por el desagüe. Por eso es una experiencia muy lujosa."

msgctxt "8600_Shizuka"
msgid "The opposite of this would be closed-loop hot springs, where they recycle the water."
msgstr "Lo contrario de esto serían las aguas termales de circuito cerrado, donde reciclan el agua."

msgctxt "8612_Kiryu"
msgid "Is that how it works..."
msgstr "¿Así es como funciona..."

msgctxt "8624_Shizuka"
msgid "Hehehe. You pretend to know more than you actually do sometimes, huh? I'm glad I got to see that surprising side of you. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Je, je, je. Suele actuar como si supiera más de lo que en realidad sabe, ¿verdad? Me alegro de haber podido ver ese lado sorprendente de usted. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8636_Kiryu"
msgid "It means all the water is pumped in directly from the ground and isn't recycled. They can only do it with springs that have a lot of output. It's pretty rare."
msgstr "Significa que toda el agua se bombea directamente del suelo y no se recicla. Sólo pueden hacerlo con aguas termales que tengan mucha salida. Es bastante raro."

msgctxt "8648_Shizuka"
msgid "I'm surprised you knew! The opposite of a hot spring straight from the source would be a closed-loop hot spring, where they recycle the water."
msgstr "Me sorprende que lo supiera. Lo contrario de una fuente termal directa sería una fuente termal de circuito cerrado, donde reciclan el agua."

msgctxt "8660_Shizuka"
msgid "I thought you didn't have much interest in these things! I'm a little shocked, to be honest. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "¡Para ser honesta con usted, no pensé que le interesaran estas cosas! Estoy un poco sorprendida <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8672_Kiryu"
msgid "Heh, I guess it could be somewhat surprising."
msgstr "Je, supongo que puedo llegar a ser algo sorprendente."

msgctxt "8684_Kiryu"
msgid "It means a hot spring where they recycle the water that comes straight out of the ground. We're living in environmentally conscious times, and water's a precious resource."
msgstr "Significa aguas termales donde reciclan el agua que sale directamente de la tierra. Vivimos en tiempos de conciencia ecológica, y el agua es un recurso precioso."

msgctxt "8696_Shizuka"
msgid "...Umm, I really hate to say this, but this hot spring is the complete opposite of what you just said..."
msgstr "...Umm, realmente odio decir esto, pero esta fuente termal es todo lo contrario de lo que acaba de decir..."

msgctxt "8708_Kiryu"
msgid "...Huh?"
msgstr "... ¿Eh?"

msgctxt "8720_Shizuka"
msgid "\"Straight from the source\" means the water is taken straight from the source, then after it's used, it's discarded. It's wasteful, but extremely luxurious..."
msgstr "\"Directamente de la fuente\" significa que el agua se extrae directamente de la fuente y, una vez utilizada, se desecha. Es un desperdicio, pero uno extremadamente lujoso..."

msgctxt "8732_Shizuka"
msgid "I'm sorry, I should care more about the environment, like you do, but I just got so excited about this place..."
msgstr "Lo siento, debería preocuparme más por el medio ambiente, como lo hace usted, pero es que me emocioné tanto con este lugar..."

msgctxt "8744_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh, no, I mean, sometimes it's good to be a bit wasteful and treat yourself. Being green is important, but it's exhausting to worry about the environment all the time, right?"
msgstr "Oh, no, quiero decir, a veces es bueno ser un poco derrochador y darse un capricho. Ser ecológico es importante, pero es agotador preocuparse por el medio ambiente todo el tiempo, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "8756_Shizuka"
msgid "Sir... Hehe. I know you're just saying that to make me feel better, but it really does. Thanks. You're so sweet. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Sir... Hehe. I know you're just saying that to make me feel better, but it really does. Thanks. You're so sweet. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8828_Kiryu"
msgid "Hot springs are great. It feels like all the exhaustion is melting off my body."
msgstr "Las aguas termales son geniales. Se siente como si todo el agotamiento se estuviera derritiendo de mi cuerpo."

msgctxt "8840_Shizuka"
msgid "When you say things like that, you sound a little bit like an old man. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Cuando dices cosas así, suenas un poco como un anciano. <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8852_amb_onsen"
msgid "I suppose I'm getting to that age where it wouldn't be weird for me to have a kid."
msgstr "Supongo que estoy llegando a esa edad en la que no sería raro para mí tener un hijo."

msgctxt "8864_Shizuka"
msgid "Haha. ♪ The image of you taking a bath with a child is a bit amusing."
msgstr "Jaja. ♪ La imagen de usted tomando un baño con un niño es un poco divertida."

msgctxt "8876_Shizuka"
msgid "I used to take baths with my father when I was young."
msgstr "Solía bañarme con mi padre cuando era joven."

msgctxt "8888_Shizuka"
msgid "I get dizzy very quickly when I get in the bath, so my father was always worried about me... <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "Me mareo muy rápido cuando me meto en el baño, así que mi padre siempre estaba preocupado por mí... <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "8900_Kiryu"
msgid "That right?"
msgstr "Con que así fue."

msgctxt "8912_Kiryu"
msgid "(Shizuka gets dizzy really easily, huh...)"
msgstr "(Shizuka se marea muy fácilmente, eh...)"

msgctxt "8924_amb_onsen"
msgid "Yeah. I want my grandchildren to wash my back for me."
msgstr "Sí. Quiero que mis nietos me laven la espalda."

msgctxt "8936_Shizuka"
msgid "I know you'd like a grandchild to do it for you, but if you'd like, I would gladly wash your back for you."
msgstr "Sé que le gustaría que un nieto lo hiciera por usted, pero si quiere, con mucho gusto le lavaré la espalda."

msgctxt "8948_Kiryu"
msgid "Whoa, hold on."
msgstr "Whoa, hold on."

msgctxt "8960_Shizuka"
msgid "I'm just kidding! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default>  I've learned recently that there's a proper sequence to follow when it comes to courting gentlemen. I wouldn't dare skip ahead."
msgstr "¡Estoy bromeando! <Color:255,200,200,255>♥<Color:Default> Recientemente he aprendido que hay una secuencia apropiada a seguir cuando se trata de cortejar caballeros. No me atrevería a saltármela."

msgctxt "8972_Kiryu"
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr "Oh..."

msgctxt "8984_Kiryu"
msgid "(...Shizuka washing my back...)"
msgstr "(... Shizuka lavándo mí espalda...)"

msgctxt "9032_Kiryu"
msgid "(No, no, what am I thinking about!?)"
msgstr "(No, no, ¿en qué estoy pensando?)"

msgctxt "9044_Shizuka"
msgid "I'm going to get out of the bath now."
msgstr "Voy a salir del baño ahora."

msgctxt "9092_Shizuka"
msgid "Hello? Are you listening to me?"
msgstr "¿Hola? ¿Me está escuchando?"

msgctxt "9104_Kiryu"
msgid "Yeah, I'm listening."
msgstr "Sí, te escucho."

msgctxt "9116_Shizuka"
msgid "Very well, then. I'm going to get out of the bath now."
msgstr "Muy bien, entonces. Voy a salir del baño."

msgctxt "9128_Kiryu"
msgid "Okay. I guess I'll get out, too."
msgstr "Bueno, entonces yo también saldré."

msgctxt "9176_Player"
msgid "Whew..."
msgstr "Uf..."

msgctxt "9260_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...water feels great. It's so nice to be out in the world again...)"
msgstr "(...water feels great. It's so nice to be out in the world again...)"

msgctxt "9272_amb_onsen"
msgid "(Phew. Come to think of it, I had a great time when I came here on a date before...)"
msgstr "(Phew. Come to think of it, I had a great time when I came here on a date before...)"

msgctxt "9284_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Maya said she gets dizzy pretty easily in the bath...)"
msgstr "(...Maya said she gets dizzy pretty easily in the bath...)"

msgctxt "9296_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Maya talked about getting spied on in the bath...)"
msgstr "(...Maya talked about getting spied on in the bath...)"

msgctxt "9308_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Shizuka talked about getting dizzy easily in the bath...)"
msgstr "(... Shizuka menciono algo sobre marearse fácilmente en el baño...)"

msgctxt "9320_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Shizuka said something about wanting to wash my back...)"
msgstr "(...Shizuka menciono algo sobre querer lavarme la espalda...)"

msgctxt "9332_amb_onsen"
msgid "(Phew. Come to think of it, I had a great time when I came here on a date before...)"
msgstr "(Phew. Come to think of it, I had a great time when I came here on a date before...)"

msgctxt "9344_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Rio-chan said something about getting dizzy easily in the bath...)"
msgstr "(... Rio-chan menciono algo sobre marearse fácilmente en el baño...)"

msgctxt "9356_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Rio-chan said something about her chest still growing...)"
msgstr "(...Rio-chan dijo algo sobre que sus pechos aún estan creciendo...)"

msgctxt "9368_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Noa-chan said something about taking baths with her father when she was young...)"
msgstr "(...Noa-chan menciono algo sobre bañarse con su padre cuando era joven...)"

msgctxt "9380_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Noa-chan said something about her chest still growing...)"
msgstr "(... Noa-chan dijo algo sobre el crecimiento de sus pechos...)"

msgctxt "9392_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Erena-chan said something about washing my back for me when I get older...)"
msgstr "(...Erena-chan said something about washing my back for me when I get older...)"

msgctxt "9404_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Erena-chan said something about taking baths with her father when she was young...)"
msgstr "(...Erena-chan said something about taking baths with her father when she was young...)"

msgctxt "9416_amb_onsen"
msgid "(Phew. Come to think of it, I had a great time when I came here on a date before...)"
msgstr "(Phew. Come to think of it, I had a great time when I came here on a date before...)"

msgctxt "9428_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Himeka said something about how I shouldn't peek on her in the bath...)"
msgstr "(...Himeka menciono algo sobre que no debería espiarla mientras está en el baño...)"

msgctxt "9440_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Himeka said something about her chest still growing...)"
msgstr "(... Himeka dijo algo acerca de que sus pechos aún crecían...)"

msgctxt "9452_amb_onsen"
msgid "(...Chihiro told me not to peek on her in the bath...)"
msgstr "(... Chihiro me dijo que no la espiara mientras está en el baño...)"

